    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior upholstery shows some staining and typical wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives fine, though the air conditioning is not as cold as it once was and it will likely need new tires within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, functional option for someone looking for dependable transportation at a reasonable price point.",
