      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs like a dream, and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable, comfy car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home where it'll get plenty of use. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
