      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a well-maintained 996.2 Carrera featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus for optimized torque delivery across the rev range. This unit retains its mechanical crispness, paired with a G96 6-speed manual transaxle that offers precise shift gates and a positive clutch engagement. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry to provide communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Notably, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row ceramic retrofit, and the rear main seal is dry. The cooling system has been refreshed with a low-temp thermostat and high-flow water pump to manage thermal loads effectively. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its age, the aerodynamic profile and underbody trays are intact, ensuring high-speed stability. A driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
