    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find the expected minor road chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably well-preserved; the premium upholstery shows only light bolster wear on the driver's side, and all electronic features\u2014including the navigation system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a comprehensive multi-point inspection, oil change, and brake pad replacement completed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly across the rev range, and the transmission shifts precisely without hesitation. Sold with a clean title and a full set of service records, this is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner who values a well-maintained, honest car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
